<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
If the project is built with none of the conditional features enabled (e.g. HAVE_FREEBSD_SENDFILE not defined and either HAVE_SYSCONF or _SC_IOV_MAX not defined), the body of MHD_send_init_static_vars_ becomes empty and the call MHD_send_init_static_vars_(); in MHD_init executes but has no effect. In that configuration the call is dead code because removing it would not change program behaviour.
</scenario>
